page_title: 'Customize a model with Azure OpenAI Service and the REST API'
page_description: Learn how to create your own customized model with Azure OpenAI Service by using the REST APIs.
chunk_content: List fine-tuning eventsTo examine the individual fine-tuning events that were generated during training:```bashcurl -X POST $AZURE_OPENAI_ENDPOINT/openai/fine_tuning/jobs/{fine_tuning_job_id}/events?api-version=2024-05-01-preview \  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \  -H "api-key: $AZURE_OPENAI_API_KEY" ```
